    JOB TAGS:
    
    Small red pill badges:
    
    * Sofa Delivery
    * Mattress Delivery
    * Marketplace Pickup
    * Apartment Move
    * Same Day Delivery
    
    SECTION STYLE:
    
    * Compact spacing
    * White background
    * No horizontal scrolling
