    * Fast loading
    
    CTA:
    
    At bottom show:
    
    Get a Quote in 2 Minutes
    
    Link:
    
    #express-quote
    
    MOBILE VISIBILITY:
    
    Show only when screen width is below 768px.
    
    Hide completely on desktop using responsive CSS.
    
    IMPORTANT:
    
    This section must feel like Facebook social proof.
    
    Simple.
    
    Clean.
    
    Fast.
    
    Trust building.
    
    No sliders.
    
    No carousels.
    
    No horizontal scrolling.
